foods.ingredients: DARK CHOCOLATE (UNSWEETENED CHOCOLATE, SUGAR, COCOA BUTTER, SOY LECITHIN [AN EMULSIFIER], VANILLA), MILK CHOCOLATE (SUGAR, COCOA BUTTER, DRY WHOLE MILK, UNSWEETENED CHOCOLATE, SOY LECITHIN [AN EMULSIFIER], VANILLA), SEA SALT CARAMEL (CREAM [MILK], SUGAR, CORN SYRUP, EVAPORATED MILK, STABILIZER [PALM OIL, GRANULAR SOYA LECITHIN], BUTTER [MILK], MALDON SEA SALT, SOY LECITHIN, VANILLA EXTRACT, HONEY, VITAMIN E [SOYBEAN OIL]), VINTAGE MERLOT SEA SALT.
foods.allHighlightFields: Ingredients: [PALM OIL, GRANULAR SOYA LECITHIN], BUTTER [MILK], MALDON SEA SALT, SOY LECITHIN, VANILLA EXTRACT, HONEY, VITAMIN E [SOYBEAN OIL]), VINTAGE MERLOT SEA SALT.
